# Ember image mapping

## Trigger

User asks to **map category images**, fix **missing Stage 2 images**, or wire **`category_images`** Storage → `pl_category_type_images`.

Full template: `supabase/import_templates/Leaf_Cursor_Template_Category_Image_Mapping.txt`

## Non-negotiables (learned the hard way)

1. **HEAD Storage before any DB write** — never invent `ember_{slug}_13_15m_category.png` URLs without a 200 response.
2. **Never `--allow-expected`** on `apply-category-image-map.mjs` unless founder confirms uploads are live.
3. **DB fix ≠ UI fix** — Discover caches Stage 2 copy 30m; `image_url` must be merged **fresh per request** (`getGatewayCategoryTypesByWrapperForAgeBandWithFreshImages`). **Deploy required** after mapping changes.
4. **Never use `applyDeterministicStorageCategoryImages` on Discover** — it fabricates broken URLs and blocks fallbacks when any `ember_*_category.png` is set.
5. **Resolve slugs via `v_gateway_category_types_public`** (anon-readable), not `pl_category_types` (RLS).

## ABI / Make Image Creation INPUT (non-negotiable)

In `stage2_category_type_label`, use **only**:

`$Image title: <toy or idea> $Description: <what the toy/idea is for parents>`

**Never** put art-direction prompts in Description (no “warm lighting”, “no children”, “Ember canvas”, “marketing art for…”, composition notes). Make’s template already owns visual style. Title/Description = the **focus object or play idea**, same register as Discover Stage 2 copy.

## Filename convention

Bucket: `category_images` · PNG only for new uploads.

| Scope | Pattern | Example |
|-------|---------|---------|
| Age-band (preferred) | `ember_{slug}_{token}_category.png` | `ember_cat_point_name_walks_13_15m_category.png` |
| Global fallback | `ember_{slug}_category.png` | `ember_cat_walk_with_job_category.png` |

Token: `age_band_id` with `age_` stripped, `-` → `_` (`13-15m` → `13_15m`).

Public URL: `{NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL}/storage/v1/object/public/category_images/{filename}`

## Efficient workflow

### 1) Preflight (read-only)

```bash
node web/scripts/preflight-category-image-map.mjs 13-15m cat_slug_one cat_slug_two ...
```

Or build a verified manifest JSON and run:

```bash
node web/scripts/fix-category-image-map.mjs 13-15m agent-tools/exports/<band>_category_image_verified_map.json
```

Manifest shape: `[{ "slug": "cat_foo", "file": "ember_cat_foo_13_15m_category.png" }]` — use `"file": null` when no object exists (deactivate, don't guess).

**Preflight table:** slug · age_band_id · category_type_id · expected_filename · HEAD 200? · action

If slug has no PNG but a **related** slug does (crosswalk), put the **verified filename** in the manifest — do not point DB at missing slug-specific names.

### 2) SQL migration

- Idempotent: deactivate superseded active rows for `(category_type_id, age_band_id)`, insert one active row.
- Write `age_band_id = '<band>'` for Discover age-scoped cards (not global) unless only global file exists.
- Mirror to `supabase/sql/` + `supabase/migrations/`; apply: `supabase db push --include-all`.

### 3) Verify (all three)

| Layer | Check |
|-------|--------|
| Storage | HEAD each mapped URL → **200** |
| DB | `v_gateway_category_type_images` → one active row per scope |
| UI | View-source on `/discover/{month}?wrapper=…` — URL must match Storage, not stale `_{token}_` ghost |

Spot-check: `/discover/14` (13–15m). Grey card = broken URL in HTML or missing PNG — fetch production HTML if user reports miss after DB push.

### 4) Export gaps

```bash
node web/scripts/export-stage2-no-image-band.mjs 13-15m
```

## Discover read path (do not regress)

```
getGatewayCategoryTypesByWrapperForAgeBandWithFreshImages  →  applyResolvedStorageCategoryImages
```

- Fresh images: `getGatewayCategoryTypeImages` in `gateway-cache.ts`
- HEAD validate + probe fallbacks: `categoryImageOverrides.ts`
- Cards read `image_url` via `categoryTypesToPlayIdeaItems` → `DiscoverFigmaImage`

## Scripts (reuse, don't rewrite)

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `web/scripts/preflight-category-image-map.mjs` | HEAD probe + slug resolve |
| `web/scripts/apply-category-image-map.mjs` | Generate migration from slugs (storage-confirmed only) |
| `web/scripts/fix-category-image-map.mjs` | Generate migration from verified manifest JSON |
| `web/scripts/export-stage2-no-image-band.mjs` | Export cards still missing images |

## Completion criteria

- Every mapped slug: HEAD 200 on `image_url` in `v_gateway_category_type_images`
- No duplicate active rows per `(category_type_id, age_band_id)`
- Skipped slugs reported with exact upload filename expected
- `PROGRESS.md` updated; user told **deploy** is required for Discover to pick up changes
